  <title>My DocBook Test 2</title>
  <section xml:id="introduction">
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
      This is a test to find out the minimal features supported by the
      Cuis Erudite Help System. The text is given in Markdown and
      converted to DocBook XML with pandoc.
    </para>
  </section>
